This is a sinmple uptime applet.

It is designed for the GNOME panel and is untested elsewhere.
Read the LICENSE file that you should have gotton with this 
program.

This has been updated to use GTK+ 2.x and GNOME 2.6+.

Even though this is a .0.0.6 version it is considered completed. If you want 
improvements then feel free to make them.  Although it may not required
by the license it is recommended that any additions are sent back to me the 
author so that I have a change to integrate them.  Also any bug reports
as well as fixes should also be sent back to me as the author.

This software is licensed under the GPL.

To install this software see the install file.

NOTE: the meminfo applets does not work in gnome 2.x

